pageContext.claim: “I go to Walter Reed on Friday and I do it quite often.”
pageContext.analysis: "Quite often" is not an exact term, but Trump seems to be on par with previous president's visits to Walter Reed Military Hospital, visiting roughly 7 times since taking office or about 4 times per year. Obama visited around 23 times total during his two terms in office, which rounds to roughly 3 times per year.
